  Subtasks:
    4.1 Create src/parsers/base.py with:
        - class Parser(ABC) with abstract parse(path) method
        - register_parser(format: str, parser_class)
        - get_parser(format: str) → Parser
    4.2 Register:
        - MarkdownParser for .md
