        - ValidationParser for validation rules
  
  Dependencies: REQ-001, REQ-002, REQ-003
  Acceptance Criteria:
    ✓ Base class is abstract
    ✓ All parsers inherit from base
    ✓ Registry works (register then get)
    ✓ Can auto-detect format from file extension
  
  Estimated Effort: 1.5 hours
  Priority: P1

