COVERAGE-001: Implement Coverage Report Generator
  Type: Implementation
  Description:
    Calculate coverage metrics: acceptance criteria, validation, [optional] API.
    Report adapts based on whether OpenAPI was provided to the generator.
  
  Subtasks:
    1.1 Create src/generators/coverage.py with:
        - build_coverage_report(test_cases, requirements, [optional] api_spec, constraints) → CoverageReport
        - calculate_acceptance_coverage(test_cases, requirements) → (percent, uncovered)
        - calculate_validation_coverage(test_cases, constraints) → (percent, by_field)
        - calculate_api_coverage([optional] test_cases, api_spec) → (percent, status_codes) or None
        - validate_100_percent_coverage(report) → bool
    1.2 Report structure (always included):
        - acceptanceCriteriaCoverage: { total, covered, percent, uncovered: str[] }
        - validationCoverage: { total_rules, covered_rules, percent, by_field: Dict }
        - testCaseSummary: { total, by_intent: { positive, negative, boundary, validation, contract[optional] } }
        - openApiIncluded: boolean flag
    1.3 Report structure (conditional on OpenAPI):
        - [IF OpenAPI provided] apiCoverage: { total_endpoints, covered_endpoints, percent, status_codes_covered: int[] }
        - [IF OpenAPI absent] apiCoverage: null (omitted from report)
    1.4 Success criteria:
        - [ALWAYS] Must achieve 100% acceptance criteria coverage
        - [ALWAYS] Must achieve 100% validation coverage (if validation rules provided)
        - [CONDITIONAL] Must achieve 100% API coverage (only validated if OpenAPI provided)
  
  Dependencies: CORE-001, DESIGN-001
  Acceptance Criteria:
    ✓ [ALWAYS] Calculates correct acceptance criteria percentages (100.0 for full coverage)
    ✓ [ALWAYS] Calculates correct validation percentages (100.0 for full coverage)
    ✓ [ALWAYS] Lists uncovered requirements
    ✓ [ALWAYS] Breaks down validation by field
    ✓ [CONDITIONAL] Calculates API coverage correctly (if OpenAPI provided)
    ✓ [CONDITIONAL] Reports status codes covered (if OpenAPI provided)
    ✓ [CONDITIONAL] Sets openApiIncluded=true when API spec exists
    ✓ [CONDITIONAL] Sets openApiIncluded=false when API spec is None (omits apiCoverage)
    ✓ [ALWAYS] Total test count and intent breakdown accurate
    ✓ Success criteria validation: 100% of applicable metrics (based on openApiIncluded)
  
  Estimated Effort: 3 hours
  Priority: P0
  
  Estimated Effort: 3 hours
  Priority: P0

