COVERAGE-003: Implement gaps report generation
  Type: Implementation
  Description:
    Identify and report missing/ambiguous requirements.
  
  Subtasks:
    3.1 Create src/generators/gaps.py (or part of coverage.py) with:
        - build_gaps_report(requirements, api_spec, constraints) → GapsReport
        - detect_ambiguous_language(text) → bool (flags "may", "should", "order to")
        - detect_missing_fields(schema, examples) → str[] (fields without examples)
        - detect_incomplete_api(endpoints) → str[] (missing schemas, examples)
    3.2 Report includes:
        - missingAcceptanceCriteria (if no AC sections found)
        - ambiguousBusinessRules (flagged with language keywords)
        - undefinedValidations (if no validation rules provided)
        - incompleteApiContracts (endpoints missing request/response schemas)
  
  Dependencies: CORE-001, DESIGN-001
  Acceptance Criteria:
    ✓ Detects ambiguous language in requirements
    ✓ Flags missing AC sections
    ✓ Flags missing validation rules
    ✓ Flags incomplete API specs
    ✓ Report is JSON and human-readable
  
  Estimated Effort: 2 hours
  Priority: P1

