==============================================================================
SUMMARY & DEPENDENCIES
==============================================================================

Critical Path (blockers - REQUIRED):
  Week 1: CORE-001 → CORE-002 → CORE-003 → CORE-004 → CORE-005 → CORE-006
  Week 2: REQ-001 → REQ-005 (markdown parsing is REQUIRED)
  Week 3: DESIGN-001 → DATA-001 (with api_spec=None if OpenAPI not provided)
  Week 4: GHERKIN-001 + PLAYWRIGHT-001 (parallel), TRACE-001, COVERAGE-001,
          ASSEMBLE-001, ASSEMBLE-002

Optional Track (can be added/skipped):
  Week 2: API-001 → API-004 (OpenAPI parsing; graceful skip if not needed)
  Note: If API track skipped, system still works (generates non-API tests)

Parallel tracks (can overlap):
  - Required parsers (REQ-*) can be built in parallel with core
  - [OPTIONAL] API parsers (API-*) can overlap with required parsers
  - Gherkin + Playwright adapters can be built in parallel
  - Unit tests can be written as soon as code is ready (not blocking)

MVP Rule Compliance:
  ✓ System works with ONLY markdown (no OpenAPI required)
  ✓ If OpenAPI provided → API Contract tests generated
  ✓ If OpenAPI absent → API tests skipped, other tests generated normally
  ✓ Functional, Validation, Boundary tests ALWAYS generated
  ✓ Gherkin, Playwright, Traceability, Coverage ALWAYS generated
  ✓ Manifest flags openApiIncluded for transparency

Estimated Total Effort:

  REQUIRED TRACK:
  - Core infrastructure: 14 hours
  - Required parsers: 11 hours (REQ-001 to REQ-005)
  - Generators: 20 hours
  - Adapters: 13 hours
  - Assembly & E2E tests: 11 hours
  - Documentation & polish: 2 hours
  Subtotal (REQUIRED): ~71 hours

  OPTIONAL TRACK (if OpenAPI used):
  - Optional parsers: 7 hours (API-001, API-002, API-004)
  - Total with OpenAPI: ~78 hours

  Total: ~71-78 hours (~18-20 days @ 4 hours/day, or ~9-10 days @ 8 hours/day)

Success Criteria:
  ✓ Phase 1 MVP complete and working end-to-end
  ✓ Works with User Stories + Acceptance Criteria only (OpenAPI optional)
  ✓ All REQUIRED components have > 90% unit test coverage
  ✓ Deterministic output verified (run twice → identical checksums)
  ✓ 100% acceptance criteria coverage [ALWAYS]
  ✓ 100% validation coverage [ALWAYS]
  ✓ 100% API coverage [CONDITIONAL on OpenAPI provided]
  ✓ All artifacts valid (Gherkin syntax, TypeScript compilation, JSON parse)
  ✓ Anti-hallucination verified (no invented fields/endpoints/constraints)
  ✓ Documentation complete
  ✓ Integration tests verify both WITH and WITHOUT OpenAPI scenarios

Ready to start Week 1? Confirm and we'll begin with CORE-001.

